@picnixz plans to write a PR to fix this issue.

I confirm that the proposed fix works as expected:

```diff
diff --git a/Modules/_sqlite/connection.c b/Modules/_sqlite/connection.c
index af63271b9fd..76df1089ebb 100644
--- a/Modules/_sqlite/connection.c
+++ b/Modules/_sqlite/connection.c
@@ -2198,7 +2198,7 @@ pysqlite_connection_create_collation_impl(pysqlite_Connection *self,
          * the context before returning.
          */
         if (callable != Py_None) {
-            free_callback_context(ctx);
+            decref_callback_context(ctx);
         }
         set_error_from_db(self->state, self->db);
         return NULL;
```
